{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"window.onload","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propiedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onerror\"><code>onerror</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/ongotpointercapture\"><code>ongotpointercapture</code></a></li><li><em><code>onload</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadeddata\"><code>onloadeddata</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadedmetadata\"><code>onloadedmetadata</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadend\"><code>onloadend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadstart\"><code>onloadstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onlostpointercapture\"><code>onlostpointercapture</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onpause\"><code>onpause</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplay\"><code>onplay</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplaying\"><code>onplaying</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Sumario","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Un evento tipo handler para el evento&nbsp;<code>load</code> event de el <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>window</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">window.onload = <em>funcRef</em>;\n</pre>\n<ul>\n <li><code>funcRef</code>&nbsp;es la función tipo handler function a ser llamada cuando el evento&nbsp;<code>load</code>&nbsp; de window se dispara.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">doSomethingElse</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Ejemplo Onload<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">load</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"evento load detectado!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onload <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> load<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>El Evento load se dispara cuando el documento ha terminado de cargarse!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notas","isH3":true,"content":"<p>El evento&nbsp;<code>load</code>&nbsp;dispara el evento al final del proceso de carga del documento. En este punto, todos los objetos del documento son DOM, &nbsp;y todas las imágenes y sub-frames han terminado de cargarse.</p>\n<p>Existen también los &nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/Gecko-Specific_DOM_Events\" title=\"en/Gecko-Specific_DOM_Events\">Eventos DOM Específicos</a>&nbsp;como&nbsp;<code>DOMContentLoaded</code>&nbsp;y&nbsp;<code>DOMFrameContentLoaded</code> (los cuales pueden ser manejados usando <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"La documentación acerca de este tema no ha sido escrita todavía . ¡Por favor  considera contribuir !\"><code>element.addEventListener()</code></a>) y son ejecutados despues de que el DOM de la página ha sido construido, pero no esperear a que otros recursos terminen de cargar.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Especificación","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Este evento tipo handler se encuentra especificado en <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/html/#handler-window-onload\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver También","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>\n  <div class=\"syntaxbox\" id=\"sect1\">\n   Evento&nbsp;<code>DOMContentLoaded</code>&nbsp;en&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/Listening_to_events#simple_dom.c2.a0events\" title=\"En/Listening to events#Simple DOM.c2.a0events\">Escuchando los Evento:Eventos DOM Simples</a></div>\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Un evento tipo handler para el evento load event de el window.","popularity":0.0034,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onload","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onload/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers","title":"GlobalEventHandlers"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload","title":"window.onload"}],"pageTitle":"window.onload - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}